</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-43_ pf-text-1"><strong>Traumatic Brain Injury (TBI) </strong>- Any injury to the brain caused by an external force, such as a bump, blow, or penetrating object.







